reviewText: Bought as a gift for my mom.  She is happy with it

ok. to be  honest ive have not seen the video. but i have sen the movie on television. its been a long time and when its on tv its called the deserter. it a excellent flick all action from start to finish. with chuck conners and richard crenna and the star bekim fehmiu and the rest of the cast all well known actors at the time fehmiu is not well known here in the usa but what few movies ive seen him in i liked. if you like indian fights you'll like this one.
